com.im.njams.sdk.client

Class LMFTEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.client.LMFTEntry

  • public class LMFTEntry
extends Object
    Configuration Entry for the LogMessageFlushTask for every Njams instance. Holds the flush size and the flush interval values for every instance.
    Author:
    pnientiedt
